api_list.name: Fact for specific number
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://testing761.p.rapidapi.com/{number}/math"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "testing761.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
api_list.body: 7 is the smallest number of sides of a regular polygon that is not constructible by straightedge and compass.
